Package: oncofix
Version: 2.0.0
Section: healthcare
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Installed-Size: 210000
Depends: nodejs (>= 18.0.0), python3 (>= 3.8), python3-venv, sqlite3
Recommends: rabbitmq-server
Maintainer: OncoFix Team <support@oncofix.com>
Description: OncoFix - Oral Cancer Screening Platform
 OncoFix is an offline-first healthcare application for oral cancer
 screening on Debian devices (OrangePi5, Raspberry Pi, etc).
 .
 Components:
  - NestJS backend API (port 3000)
  - React frontend SPA (port 5173 via serve)
  - MONAI AI cancer prediction model
  - SQLite local storage with BigQuery sync
 .
 Sync: offline-first, syncs to BigQuery every 5 min when internet available.
 RabbitMQ is optional - sync falls back to direct BigQuery insert.
